== 案件后续 ==
陈果仁被葬于[[底特律|底特律]]的森林草坪公墓（{{lang|en|Forest Lawn Cemetery}}）<ref>{{cite news |last=Lewis |first=Shawn D. |url=http://www.detroitnews.com/article/20120621/METRO/206210385 |title=30 years later, Vincent Chin's family awaits justice in fatal beating |work={{Link-en|底特律新闻报|The Detroit News}} |date=2012-06-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202145601/http://www.detroitnews.com/article/20120621/METRO/206210385 |archivedate=2014-02-02 |accessdate=2020-10-08 }}</ref>。

为了避免回忆起这起谋杀案，陈果仁的母亲陈余琼芳在1987年9月从橡树公园搬回了她的故乡[[广州市|广州市]]。2001年下半年，陈余琼芳因病回到美国治疗；2002年6月9日，她病重不治。在她去世之前，陈余琼芳建立了一个纪念陈果仁的奖学金并委托美国公民正义组织（{{lang|en|American Citizens for Justice}}）负责管理<ref>{{cite news |url=http://iis.stat.wright.edu/AAC-Dayton/news_reported/memorial_LilyChin.htm |title=OCA Mourns Death Of Lily Chin |work=Asian American Council |date=2002-06-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507131750/http://iis.stat.wright.edu/AAC-Dayton/index.htm |archivedate=2016-05-07 |accessdate=2020-10-12 }}</ref>。

